brdm1 = pd.DataFrame(index=conditions, columns=conditions)
brdm1.fillna(0)

for i in range(len(conditions)):
    for j in range(len(conditions)):
        brdm1.loc[conditions[i], conditions[j]] = np.abs(rt_data[i] - rt_data[j])


brdm1 = brdm1.astype(float)

brdm1 = Adjacency(brdm1, matrix_type='distance', labels=conditions)

Subject level¶

In [65]:
all_sub_dissim = {}; all_sub_mrdm1_rsa = {}; all_sub_mrdm2_rsa = {}; all_sub_brdm1_rsa = {}
for subj in subjs_list:
    file_list = glob.glob(os.path.join(data_dir, subj, f'beta*nii.gz'))
    file_list.sort()
    print('Calculating dissimilarities for '+subj)

    #conditions = [os.path.basename(x)[:-7].split('_beta_')[-1] for x in file_list]

    beta = Brain_Data(file_list)
    
    
    sub_pattern_dissim = beta.apply_mask(mask).distance(metric='correlation')
    #sub_pattern_similarity.data = 1 - sub_pattern_similarity.data
    sub_pattern_dissim.labels = conditions
    s_mrdm1 = sub_pattern_dissim.similarity(mrdm1, metric='spearman', n_permute=0)
    s_mrdm2 = sub_pattern_dissim.similarity(mrdm2, metric='spearman', n_permute=0)
    s_brdm1 = sub_pattern_dissim.similarity(brdm1, metric='spearman', n_permute=0)

    
    all_sub_dissim[subj] = sub_pattern_dissim
    all_sub_mrdm1_rsa[subj] = s_mrdm1['correlation']
    all_sub_mrdm2_rsa[subj] = s_mrdm2['correlation']
    all_sub_brdm1_rsa[subj] = s_brdm1['correlation']
all_sub_mrdm1_rsa = pd.DataFrame(all_sub_mrdm1_rsa, index=['r', 'p']).T
all_sub_mrdm2_rsa = pd.DataFrame(all_sub_mrdm2_rsa, index=['r', 'p']).T
all_sub_brdm1_rsa = pd.DataFrame(all_sub_brdm1_rsa, index=['r', 'p']).T
